files.patch:
@@ -32,4 +32,1 @@
-TMPFILE=`mktemp`
-OUT=`. $DIR/autoconf-config.guess 2> "$TMPFILE"`
-ERR=`cat "$TMPFILE"`
-rm "$TMPFILE"
+OUT=`. $DIR/autoconf-config.guess 2> /dev/null`
@@ -63,1 +60,2 @@
-    echo $ERR >&2
+    # Run autoconf-config.guess again to get the error message.
+    . $DIR/autoconf-config.guess > /dev/null
